tals\' style=\'width: 100%; font-size: 14px;\'>\n                                    <tr><td style=\'padding: 4px 0; color: #64748b;\'>Subtotal:</td><td style=\'text-align: right; color: #0f172a;\'>₱145.00</td></tr>\n                                    <tr><td style=\'padding: 4px 0; color: #ef4444;\'>Discount (0%):</td><td style=\'text-align: right; color: #ef4444;\'>-₱0.00</td></tr>\n                                    <tr><td style=\'padding: 15px 0 4px; color: #4f46e5; font-size: 18px; font-weight: 700;\'>Total Amount Paid:</td><td style=\'text-align: right; color: #4f46e5; font-size: 18px; font-weight: 700;\'>₱145.00</td></tr>\n                                    <tr><td style=\'padding: 4px 0; color: #64748b;\'>Cash Received:</td><td style=\'text-align: right; color: #0f172a;\'>₱145.00</td></tr>\n                                    <tr><td style=\'padding: 4px 0; color: #64748b;\'>Change:</td><td style=\'text-align: right; color: #0f172a;\'>₱0.00</td></tr>\n                                </table>\n                            </div>\n\n                            <div style=\'margin-top: 32px; padding: 18px 14px; background-color: #eff6ff; border-radius: 12px; text-align: center;\'>\n                                <p style=\'margin: 0; color: #1e40af; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 500;\'>Thank you for choosing Granby College of Science and Technology!</p>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\'receipt-footer\' style=\'background-color: #f8fafc; padding: 22px 18px; text-align: center; border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0;\'>\n                            <p style=\'margin: 0; color: #64748b; font-size: 12px;\'>© 2026 Granby Colleges of Science and Technology. All rights reserved.</p>\n                            <p style=\'margin: 8px 0 0; color: #94a3b8; font-size: 11px; line-height: 1.4;\'>This is an automated system notification regarding your recent transaction. Please do not reply directly to this